A June 2019 snapshot of [Paul Wilson](/Paul_Wilson_(musician)) and [Gary Lightbody](/Gary_Lightbody), caught in the act of performing at [Werchter Boutique](/Werchter_Boutique). The show, it seems, must always go on.

